的需求是开新能源车就是要节约燃料成本（每天通勤 100km ），那么理想的纯电续航（ 200km ）是否就变成了劣势？", "last_modified": 1734768944, "replies": 34, "id": 1099285}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "/static/img/node_default_large.png", "name": "immigration", "avatar_normal": "/static/img/node_default_normal.png", "title": "移民", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/immigration", "topics": 118, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Immigration", "avatar_mini": "/static/img/node_default_mini.png", "stars": 624, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 970, "parent_node_name": "life"}, "member": {"id": 490094, "username": "nnd", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/nnd", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/897f981688b8cfa09d999145daecba5c?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/897f981688b8cfa09d999145daecba5c?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/897f981688b8cfa09d999145daecba5c?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1589774084, "last_modified": 1699880651}, "last_reply_by": "lihua", "last_touched": 1734827808, "title": "为什么会有人移民马来西亚？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1099297", "created": 1734773895, "deleted": 0, "content": "以前公司的领导，两千年前移民去了香港，去年又移民去了马拉西亚。\r\n马来西亚对比香港护照有啥优势，想不明白为啥要移民去马拉西亚？", "content_rendered": "<p>以前公司的领导，两千年前移民去了香港，去年又移民去了马拉西亚。\n马来西亚对比香港护照有啥优势，想不明白为啥要移民去马拉西亚？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1734773895, "replies": 34, "id": 1099297}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_large.png?m=1649080598", "name": "macos", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_normal.png?m=1649080598", "title": "macOS", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/macos", "topics": 22565, "footer": "<a href=\"/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 等 <a href=\"/go/apple\">Apple</a> 公司设计的计算机所运行的操作系统。<a href=\"/go/idev\">iOS</a> 的基础。", "header": "The world’s most advanced desktop operating system.", "title_alternative": "macOS", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b6d7/67d2/22_mini.png?m=1649080598", "stars": 5307, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 22, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"id": 661456, "username": "Kakarottoxxxx", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Kakarottoxxxx", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/271db036a35356aa2efc92e1b7b20b22?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/271db036a35356aa2efc92e1b7b20b22?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/271db036a35356aa2efc92e1b7b20b22?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1699518268, "last_modified": 1734831324}, "last_reply_by": "hsulin", "last_touched": 1734840442, "title": "3 年 50 次迭代：我编写了一款专为 Mac 打造的休息提醒工具", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1099352", "created": 1734832151, "deleted": 0, "content": "三年前，我开始开发 macOS 休息提醒工具 Eye Monitor ，目前这款应用已经常驻在 App Store 健康榜的前三位。\r\n\r\nEye Monitor 的设计初衷是因为本人常常面对电脑一工作就是 3 、4 小时不停歇，长时间的用眼和久坐导致我在某个时期视力下降明显以及出现腰酸的现象。\r\n\r\nEye Monitor 工作原理很简单：它通过你在 Mac 上的鼠标移动和键盘使用来自动识别你是否在使用电脑，并在长时间使用后弹出弹窗提醒你休息。所以你不需要手动地设置提醒。\r\n\r\n这三年进行不少功能迭代，其中我最喜欢的功能有三个：\r\n1 、数据报表：可以查看历史上使用时长、休息完成率等数据的趋势，并且数据可以通过 iCloud 同步，也可以下载到本地\r\n2 、自定义全屏弹窗的壁纸和提示词：颜值即正义\r\n3 、iOS 提醒：我发现自己常常在 Eye Monitor 提示我休息后离开电脑开始玩手机，可以称之为“假休息”。所以我也写了一个 iOS 版本，用来接收 Mac 的提醒并在手机上也弹出提醒，这样可以让我回头是岸。\r\n\r\n\r\n清华大学有句口号叫做“为祖国健康工作五十年”，希望大家共勉之。", "content_rendered": "三年前，我开始开发 macOS 休息提醒工具 Eye Monitor ，目前这款应用已经常驻在 App Store 健康榜的前三位。<br /><br />Eye Monitor 的设计初衷是因为本人常常面对电脑一工作就是 3 、4 小时不停歇，长时间的用眼和久坐导致我在某个时期视力下降明显以及出现腰酸的现象。<br /><br />Eye Monitor 工作原理很简单：它通过你在 Mac 上的鼠标移动和键盘使用来自动识别你是否在使用电脑，并在长时间使用后弹出弹窗提醒你休息。所以你不需要手动地设置提醒。<br /><br />这三年进行不少功能迭代，其中我最喜欢的功能有三个：<br />1 、数据报表：可以查看历史上使用时长、休息完成率等数据的趋势，并且数据可以通过 iCloud 同步，也可以下载到本地<br />2 、自定义全屏弹窗的壁纸和提示词：颜值即正义<br />3 、iOS 提醒：我发现自己常常在 Eye Monitor 提示我休息后离开电脑开始玩手机，可以称之为“假休息”。所以我也写了一个 iOS 版本，用来接收 Mac 的提醒并在手机上也弹出提醒，这样可以让我回头是岸。<br /><br /><br />清华大学有句口号叫做“为祖国健康工作五十年”，希望大家共勉之。", "last_modified": 1734832151, "replies": 31, "id": 1099352}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1695370146", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1695370146", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 18826, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1695370146", "stars": 3319, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": "work"}, "member": {"id": 317875, "username": "nathen", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/nathen", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1a3c755d302d526bf03dc85b7da549db?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1a3c755d302d526bf03dc85b7da549db?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1a3c755d302d526bf03dc85b7da549db?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1526978813, "last_modified": 1734761576}, "last_reply_by": "genesislive", "last_touched": 1734822835, "title": "大家觉得明年工作会好找些吗?", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1099320", "created": 1734784985, "deleted": 0, "content": "", "content_rendered": "", "last_modified": 1734789457, "replies": 28, "id": 1099320}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 226692, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 4285, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 394310, "username": "owlzhang95", "url"